snippet.title: DurDanto Official Gameplay Trailer #2
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1602370/DurDanto/
Demo available on Steam. Wishlist now!

DurDanto is a pixel art metroidvania game where you play as Zubok in a fallen city with beautiful pixel art environments while facing different enemies.
